{"id": "1445416838208164113", "channel_id": "1445416838208164113", "type": 0, "author_id": "404645235197607939", "author_name": "wilson_1024", "author_bot": false, "content": "第1队是以鸟哥鸟弟为主，医生负责银饰充能开觉醒，剩下1个位置打算塞温可尔解决狂气问题。\n但是塞了 雷亚 后可以获得血胎来解决狂气，而且鸟哥也可以吃到新密契的“卡牌进入空间加血肉进度”的效果来加速自身的狂气。\n然后主流配队大多数是塞 诗人 的，可是我的 诗人 塞了进去 第二队打反击流，主要是诗人有“反击提升”和降力效果。\n然后第3张图就是我其他的一些辅助，目前无就业空间\n所以鸟哥鸟弟带什么辅助好啊", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T14:10:28.775000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445416839315198026", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-01-270_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 219159, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445416838208164113/1445416839315198026/Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-01-270_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=6a01e355&is=6a0091d5&hm=0559590bedb1ca7cc59f4cf31ddfe6f3cb99bc20a80e635b82dea44d04c0b340&"}, {"id": "1445416840410038322", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-04-670_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 209404, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445416838208164113/1445416840410038322/Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-04-670_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=6a01e355&is=6a0091d5&hm=edc8efb2782897d393f94bfae80cdb3c79611d354a9aebef8b31750dde6db45d&"}, {"id": "1445416841244573708", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-54-15-621_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 192175, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445416838208164113/1445416841244573708/Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-54-15-621_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=6a01e355&is=6a0091d5&hm=1d72c03149cfd342b1e73294deb4686f9d3055f1080147fb86fd870f8d2a64b7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445416838208164113", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾配队（辅助疑惑）", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1445334431920296027", "channel_id": "1445334431920296027", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139202390919233566", "author_name": "akkom730", "author_bot": false, "content": "咳咳…我…我不行了\n剩下的…就交給你了！(趴\n\n媽呀我討厭破眼球\n不要吃我狂啦，我沒狂開大啊啊啊\n\n建議攻略：\n老招\n借一隻塔薇(70等有超限)+3隻廢物\n# 3隻廢物\n然後密契塞上去，具體作用不是很重要，大方向為銀鑰疊高就好\n\n# 講點操作的問題\n這波的眼球效果是\n每回合減少我方10狂，回870左右的血\n如果沒有穩定的狂氣收入，你開不了大(自己回合結束+5狂對面吃你10狂，我狂啊<:takenotes:1357186646294138890> \n造物功能是大招出傷強化，每次開大依照消耗狂氣量給銀鑰，並減少狂氣上限20(最多5次\n\n我是非主C有狂就開，每隊盡量塞一隻自充很快的角色\n覺醒先給塔薇，接下來等開第一次大(超限)再慢慢覺醒其他人\n\n如果隊伍操作不夠熟悉會打很久，我平均10t以上到14t", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T08:43:01.585000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1445334432830722168", "filename": "IMG_4511.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1171850, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445334431920296027/1445334432830722168/IMG_4511.png?ex=6a019695&is=6a004515&hm=753d4ad0f16eee55d3cce690e2fff228ab279735319265d434cdb78a1f0793a3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445334431920296027", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "大眼球D2", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444", "is_thread_starter": true}
